Package org.opengrok.indexer.history

Class CacheException

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Throwable
java.lang.Exception
org.opengrok.indexer.history.CacheException
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CacheException extends Exception
Exception thrown when retrieval or manipulation of cache data fails. This is used for implementations of HistoryCache and AnnotationCache.
